      <div class="fq-q">How do I get to the Príncipe Felipe Science Museum?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">The museum is at Av. del Professor López Piñero, 7, 46013 Valencia. Metro lines 3 and 5 stop at Alameda station (15 min walk). Bus lines 13, 14, 15, 19, 35, 40, and 95 serve the complex. Parking is available on-site at €2.30/hr (max €24/day, or €7/day with ticket purchase).</div>
